---
title: Thai Style Chicken & Bell Pepper Noodle Dinner to Thai Style Chicken & Rice Bowl Lunch
description: We love Thai style chicken, and this deliciously simple, chef-curated recipe doesn't disappoint. Time to bust out the pots and pans!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/asian-style-chicken-dinner-3b2613fa-d17ee14a.jpg
